Insignificant||Your people have achieved little and are of no consequence to the world - yet!
Your tributary states||These factions are under your protection. In exchange for this, you receive a tribute from them every turn and they're sworn to protect you if someone declares war on you.
As a tributary, you're under the protection of another faction. This comes at great cost though: you pay a tribute each turn and can't have tributary or puppet states while being one yourself.
